I've been married for 39 years, so this is getting to be a foreign concept.
Just goes to show how organized men are.  (Yeah ... Right) A place for everything ... and everything in its place.

I agree Rich....if that dude could see my garage right now he might think again about the box system not touching one another ...its more like ...my boxes are stacked to the perfect height of being a useful bench to put tools on ...lol...
Boxes (compartments) in the brain are different from boxes on the garage floor.  The one-track mind falls apart when put into practice.
